Jacob Zuma may be going down in history as the president who refused to step down, but he may also be the most-memed president on Twitter. As the news broke that the ANC national executive committee had decided to recall him following numerous failed attempts at negotiating his exit, South Africans took to the popular social media platform to express their thoughts on the matter. From hilarious to explosive, South Africans didn't hold back, and Twitter feeds were filled with #ZumaExit observations. It was difficult to narrow down the list of favourites, but here are 10 of the best tweets on the matter:          